---
---

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-10">
  {/* Client-side diagram */}
  <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-red-200 bg-red-50/50 p-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(220,38,38,0.15)]">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-red-700 text-center">Client-side (standardowy)</h3>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      {/* Browser */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 text-center text-sm font-medium border border-red-100 shadow-sm">
        🧑‍💻 Przeglądarka użytkownika
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-red-400 text-2xl">↓</div>

      {/* Scripts */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 text-center text-sm border border-red-100 shadow-sm">
        <span class="font-medium">gtm.js / analytics.js / fbevents.js</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-red-400 text-2xl">↓</div>

      {/* Destinations - branching */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-red-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          📊 GA4
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-red-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          📘 Meta Pixel
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-red-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          🔍 Google Ads
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Alert */}
    <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-red-100 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-700 font-medium">
        ⚠️ Adblocker / ITP = blokada na etapie przeglądarki. Dane NIE docierają.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Server-side diagram */}
  <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/50 p-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(16,185,129,0.2)]">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-emerald-700 text-center">Server-side</h3>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      {/* Browser */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 text-center text-sm font-medium border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm">
        🧑‍💻 Przeglądarka użytkownika
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-emerald-500 text-2xl">↓</div>

      {/* Server */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center border-2 border-emerald-300 shadow-md ring-2 ring-emerald-200">
        <span class="font-bold text-sm">🖥️ Twój serwer</span>
        <span class="block text-xs text-emerald-600 mt-0.5">t.twojadomena.pl (GTM SS)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-emerald-500 text-2xl">↓</div>

      {/* Destinations - branching */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          📊 GA4
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          📘 Meta CAPI
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 text-center text-xs border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm font-medium">
          🔍 Google Ads EC
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Alert */}
    <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg border border-emerald-200">
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-700 font-medium">
        ✅ Dane idą przez Twój serwer. Adblocker nie widzi. Pełna kontrola.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
